    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs required 3) is accepted given the standardized single-condition nature of ASTM F1717 and the conservative acceptance bounds applied. The FEA ensemble results are presented as primary validation evidence; the simulation outputs are argued to be functionally equivalent to a repeated experimental campaign due to calibrated boundary conditions and direct input-parameter traceability. Overall credibility is judged sufficient for a Medium model risk, Medium consequence COU at assurance level Medium.",
